description: Rules for plugin/tool implementations
globs: "plugins/**/*.py"
alwaysApply: true
---

# Plugin/Tool Rules

- All tools inherit from `BaseTool` in `plugins/base.py`
- Must have `name` and `description` attributes
- Must implement both `async execute()` and `async dry_run()` methods
- `dry_run()` simulates without side effects — required for safety
- Add unit test in `tests/unit/`
- Add entry to README plugin table
- Tools in `plugins/generated/` are NEVER auto-loaded — require explicit user approval
- Sandboxed via bubblewrap — no network access by default
